- **Preview Confirmation**: Before sending, shows confirmation modal with phone number, template info, parameter list, and SMS preview content (placeholders replaced with actual values).
- **Enhanced Results**: Test result display now includes parameter list (as Tags) and full SMS preview content, with success/error styling.

